   - **A** in position 3 → ❌ Wrong (RETURN to pool)
   - **S** in position 4 → ❌ Wrong (RETURN to pool)
   - **S** in position 5 → ❌ Wrong (RETURN to pool)
   - **O** in position 6 → ❌ Wrong (RETURN to pool)

**Result:** 
- "PIC" locked in place (blue) and can't be moved
- "ASSO" returned to letter pool to try again
- Next submission reveals more correct letters progressively

